reviewText: Son LOVED it! I knew he would! Perfect condition. Great price!
I enjoyed to watch that Duke of Hazzard and I start Collect them. Even I take them to Camping as well.

my 3 and 5 year old boys have gone thru the whole tv series (other than the cartoons) so i wanted to find more for them to watch.  i guess I should have judged this "book" by it's cover?  I spend more time fast forwarding thru the bad parts than it's worth.  not something you can toss in the machine to keep them occupied while you do something else.
1st movie was good,  2nd one of those I couldn't continue watching. Strange actors, genericness, maybe ok for a younger person.
ok movie based on TV show but not very accurate to the charters especially the car.
Mu son loves Dukes of Hazzard.
A really fun couple of movies
